Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I join?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can hardly see what's up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When's it going to stop raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be at least half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a tradesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you sell me food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain ruined all of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, this barrel's empty, and I'm not a tradesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:02:59.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you putting in there then? That's a huge barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A corpse, man, a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:17.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm traveling to take a rainbow home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us about it, tell us why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happen to be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:37.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back when I was a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenrou, grab Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again Pops, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here comes the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here comes the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honey! Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:09.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For as long as I could remember, my dad would\Nchange when he felt the rain coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:14.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd run around the mountains in joy,\Nand he wouldn't come back for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:27.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Days later he'd be found stuck in mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,or he'd have come home by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:36.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on days that it wouldn't rain,\Nhe'd chug down tons of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might as well not come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:48.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's happened to me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I've seen that rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is{\i0} no such rainbow! You've gone crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Pops,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,is it fun running around in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's too fun to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't. Mom will throw a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, tell me about the rainbow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't tell Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:31.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the day before you were born,\Nright after the flood finally settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We spent so much effort on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess we need to think it over some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's about as tough a bridge as we can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's rather clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was rooted in the riverbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say there's treasure at the end of the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:25.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the rainbow would\Nalways show itself after any rainfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would entertain my dad with different\Nshapes each time he saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to everyone else it was invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:40.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the only one that seemed to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:46.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day it showed up at a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I haven't seen it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My throat's been dry since then\Nno matter how much I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:01.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body gets tingly at times when it's about to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I come to, I'm running\Naround all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:09.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I long for the rainbow so much\Nwhen I'm normal like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want it... I just can't help but want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:22.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go look for it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,my father became ill and spent his time in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:37.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet he'd try to run wild when it was about to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:41.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eventually he became too weak to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:08:00.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So here I am traveling, trying to find the rainbow for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're going to nab that rainbow\Nwith your two hands, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't know 'til I see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the rain's settling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your story was a bit loose at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm leaving too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:39.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should go that way if you're looking for the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't just make that story up, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What your dad saw is a Mushi called Kouda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only seen it once before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I never got a chance to see it at the root.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'll tag along if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can pay me in food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That barrel of yours... just sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt it'll be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,First off,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can only see a normal rainbow when\Nyou're facing away from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kouda can appear anywhere regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, and the colors are backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be wasting your time running around\Nunless you keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginko, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a reason you're traveling too, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you helping out a stranger like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I just want to see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a specific reason to be traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess I can't be chasing a Kouda around forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give up if we can't find it by the first day of spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently  they're like normal rainbows\Nin that they appear after rainfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gotta anticipate where it's gonna rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gotten pretty savvy at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like it'll rain here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mountain over there has a "hat".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to rain there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've been wandering around blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's just a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did expect it, but it's going to be hard to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long have you been traveling for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, that story of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,About wanting to show it to your ill dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lied, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:29.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe you'd leave your family\Nwith an ill man for five years to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that I want to show it to my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that might not have been why I started doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't told you my name, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kourou is the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:48.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a name that traps me to the shame\Nof my father's rainbow chasing fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the laughingstock of the village because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a river in the country up north,\Nfamous for its turbulent waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm from a family of engineers that've been\Nbuilding bridges across it for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As many times as we'd build bridges, they'd\Nget destroyed during the high tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone had high hopes for my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My older brother took his place with his brilliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd design a sturdier bridge each time it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:21.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a speck of the talent that he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:28.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost coordination in my left hand\Never since I cut a tendon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm useless even as a carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:38.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I had no place\Nin the village except by my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear it, so I ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then why is it that you're looking for the rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but go after it every time I saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For one I wanted to see if what my dad said was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to prove to the people in town\Nthat it was all because of the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter where I go, I'm still a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:25.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even stay alive without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A reason, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you're traveling without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you must have a reason though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traveling isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't go on traveling without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes I want to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I just {\i1}make{\i0} a reason, like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way breaks just come naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have "breaks" when you're just "staying alive".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking all this seriously, and you think it's a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it seriously too, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking a break is important to living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think it's a better motive than what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:20.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just condemning yourself to chasing\Na rainbow so you can drown out your guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:27.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have just settled down somewhere\Nand forgotten your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here now because I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But maybe it's time I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll quit when spring comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got good eyes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are a mermaid's nails. Mix them\Nin water and you'll have a love potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make it cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything to make it rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All these back to back sunny\Ndays are drying up the crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd have used it myself if there were such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,keep watch on the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about time it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even sweat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes the rain, here comes the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:05.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun's under the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait. The love potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry man, it's closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't rush off so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It still looks like it's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might not have gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew where it was going to rain without even looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it like this for Dad too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kourou,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:16.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you must be getting to despise me\Nand the name I gave you by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:25.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you the name of the\Nmost beautiful thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get laughed at by your friends because of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought of a better name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call yourself by it from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:18:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become an even better engineer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, it's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the name of the most beautiful thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:29.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gotta take this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:03.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure until now, but it's tingling on my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a type of Nagaremono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagaremono?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it has life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's a {\i1}thing{\i0} close to being a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:20.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other than having life, it's the same as the "rainbow"\Nphenomenon caused by light and rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:27.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kouda must have been created\Nby light and rain containing Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the origin of Mushi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:37.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagaremono are like floods and typhoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a reason that they're created,\Nbut they bear no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They arise just to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:49.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interrupted by nothing, they leave\Nonly their influence, and are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be infected when you touch such a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:01.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For an instant, I felt like I was inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:06.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Dad was engulfed by that rising stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't have any power over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like there's a hole in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno, I'll think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like this guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just flowing away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what happened to the man since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:51.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was told that an indestructible bridge\Nwas built on the violent river of the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:58.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd detach one pillar form each bridge\Npiece and let each flow freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when the water settles, they'd reconnect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:08.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been given the name "Nagarebashi"\Nafter one man's invention.
